ID: text = sav[r]atra vijite [De]va[naṃ]priyasa Priyadraśisa y[e] ca [a]ṃta yathā [Coḍa] Paṃḍiya Satiyaputro Keraḍaputro Taṃbapaṃṇī Aṃtiyo[k]o nāma Yona-raja ye ca aṃñe tasa Aṃtiyokasa samaṃta rajano savratra Devanaṃpriyasa Priyadraśisa raño du[vi] cik[i]sa [kr]i[ṭa] manusa-cikisa .. pa[śu-c]ikisa [ca]
text = [o]śa[ḍha]ni manuśopakani ca paśopakani ca yat[r]a yatra nāsti savatra harapita ca vuta ca
text = kupa ca khanapita pratibh[o]gaye paśu-manuśanaṃ
